{"tid":593539,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【樽裝水93%含膠】Aqua、Evian等國際品牌都中招 9國調查揭嚴重污染","createTime":"2018-03-15T05:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T06:00:45.000Z","uid":33357,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"92448a137efd8b51485c8b6886958c40e41ded6d","tid":593539,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:46:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180315&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57949491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180315%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57949491&d=CfYj5Sot4Mn2GrTY8971y6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=4a150973\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180315%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57949491&h=39fd79f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180315&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57949491</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180315/large/1521091996_4851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180315%2Flarge%2F1521091996_4851.jpg&h=e129e82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國紐約州立大學一項涉及全球九個國家的大型研究發現，全球多個知名品牌的樽裝水，都被細微塑膠粒子污染，「污染情況非常廣泛」。這些細微塑膠粒子，可能是在包裝過程中滲入樽內，研究結果在周三公佈。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員在中國、美國、泰國、巴西、印度、印尼、肯雅、黎巴嫩、墨西哥共9個國家，測試250樽樽裝水。研究人員在93%樣本當中都找到塑膠，這些含塑膠的樽裝水不乏大牌子，例如是Evian、San Pellegrino、Nestle Pure Life、Aqua、Aquafina及Dasani。<br />\n<br />\n塑膠殘留種類繁多，有聚丙烯、尼龍以及俗稱「的確涼」的聚對苯二甲酸乙二酯，聚對苯二甲酸乙二酯主要用來製作樽蓋。<br />\n<br />\n帶領研究的微塑膠學家梅森（Sherri Mason）表示：「研究中我們發現的65%粒子，其實是碎片而非纖維。我認為這來自樽裝水入樽過程。」專家暫時未知情況對人類構成的威脅，但梅森警告：「這情況與部分癌症、精子數目下降以及專注力失調及過度活躍症（ADHD）和自閉症有關。」<br />\n<br />\n早前也有研究發現自來水也含有微膠粒，但梅森說：「水喉水很大程度上比樽裝水安全。」<br />\n<br />\n樽裝水殺精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飲開Evian<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719a4ad229794985d7d8189ff8312fad400324e6","tid":593539,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"磅甩誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932703e7d31d2f9ec7bc52edc392620eb494de97","tid":593539,"uid":33357,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"719a4ad229794985d7d8189ff8312fad400324e6","tid":593539,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"磅甩誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:00:45.000Z","msg":"轉飲屋企煲既水算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}